'Yan sanda sun yi arangama da 'yan 'yan tawaye a Catalonia a ranar tunawa da zaben raba gardamar 'yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Lahadi bayan masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai sun yi arangama da jami'an 'yan sanda a lokacin da dubban mutane suka shiga zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da zaben raba gardama na Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan tawaye masu rufe fuska, da 'yan sanda suka tsare, sun yi ta jefa musu ƙwai da kuma fentin foda, suna haifar da duhu a kan titunan da ke cike da masu yawon bude ido.
Daga baya a ranar, an yi arangama da 'yan sanda da suka yi amfani da sanduna don dakile faɗa.
Masu goyon bayan 'yancin kai sun yi ta rera waka na tsawon sa'o'i suna cewa "Ba za a manta da mu ba, ba za a gafarta mana ba" kuma sun yi karo da masu goyon bayan kungiyar da ke ihu "Long live Spain".
Mutane 14 sun samu magani saboda raunuka masu saurin gaske da suka samu a zanga-zangar, in ji manema labarai na yankin.
Har yanzu akwai tashin hankali a yankin da ya yanke shawarar samun 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan kuri'ar raba gardama da Madrid ta ayyana a matsayin haramtacciya amma 'yan 'yan adawar Catalonia ke murna da ita.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun fi rinjaye a zaben 'yancin kai, duk da cewa yawan masu kada kuri'a ya yi kadan saboda masu adawa da 'yancin kai sun kauracewa zaben.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane 1,000 ne suka ji rauni a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin dakatar da zaben a wasu wuraren zabe a yankin.
Kungiyoyin 'yancin kai sun yi zango a daren Juma'a don hana zanga-zangar da kuma nuna goyon baya ga 'yan sanda.
An yi zanga-zangar amma an canja hanyar.
Narcis Termes, mai shekaru 68, wani mai aikin lantarki wanda ya halarci zanga-zangar raba gardama tare da matarsa, ya ce ba shi da kwarin gwiwa game da batun 'yancin kai na Catalonia.
A shekarar da ta gabata mun samu daya daga cikin mafiya kyawun lokutanmu.
Ya ce, "Na ga iyayena suna kuka saboda farin ciki da aka ba su damar kada kuri'a, amma yanzu muna cikin matsala".
Duk da samun gagarumar nasara a zaben kananan hukumomi da aka yi a watan Disamba da ya gabata, jam'iyyun 'yancin kai na Catalonia sun yi fama da samun ci gaba saboda wasu daga cikin fitattun shugabanninsu suna gudun hijira ko kuma a tsare, suna jiran shari'a saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya kuri'ar raba gardama da kuma sanar da 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, wani mai aikin mota mai shekara 42 wanda ya yi amfani da wayar salula wajen daukar hotunan zanga-zangar da 'yan sanda ke yi, ya ce 'yan siyasa a bangarorin biyu sun ci gaba da tayar da hankali.
Ya ce, "Yanayin ya kara tsanantawa".
A ranar Asabar Oriol Junqueras, daya daga cikin shuwagabannin Catalonia tara da ke tsare tun karshen shekarar da ta gabata, ya sanar da tsayawarsa takarar zaben majalisar Turai na shekara mai zuwa.
"Tsofa takarar a zaben Turai ita ce hanya mafi kyau ta yanke hukunci kan koma bayan dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma matsin lamba da hukumomin Spain suka sanya mana", in ji shi.
