Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI
Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun karfin gwiwa a fannin kera kere, ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa a fannin binciken kere kere, in ji mai saka jari kuma mai fasaha Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan bayanin ya zo ne bayan da wasu bangarori na gwamnatin Amurka suka ba da sanarwar game da AI, kodayake Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da wata dabara ta AI.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta bayyana shirinta a bara: tana da burin zama ta farko a fannin kirkire-kirkire na wucin gadi nan da shekarar 2030.
"Sau biyu na kasafin kudin AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, la'akari da cewa duk sauran ƙasashe suna baya da Amurka, kuma muna neman sabon ci gaba a cikin AI", in ji Lee.
Karin kudade zai ninka damar da babbar nasara ta gaba a fannin kere kere za ta faru a Amurka, Lee ya fada a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna "Superpowers of Artificial Intelligence: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" ya fito daga Houghton Mifflin Harcourt a wannan watan, shi ne babban darektan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya saka hannun jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kere kere a kasar Sin, Face++.
