Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron farko na zaben a wannan karon a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin taron Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa ciki har da ziyartar wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran zabensa don cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun kolin Amurka, Trump na shirin kara samun goyon baya a zaben da ake shirin yi a tsakiyar wa'adin mulkinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki bayan zaben da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe bakwai na daren yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a ƙasa a bidiyo na YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi magana ne game da sauraron shari'ar da aka yi a wannan makon game da nadin Brett Kavanaugh a Kotun Koli, wanda ya kasance mai tsauri saboda zargin cin zarafin mata, kuma an jinkirta kuri'ar da aka yi a majalisar dattijai har tsawon mako guda har sai FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, kamfen din shugaba Trump ya ce an gudanar da taron ne a wannan makon don karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki na da matukar muhimmanci a cikin shirinsa, don haka shugaban zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa kasashe da dama kamar yadda ya kamata yayin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
An shirya taron ne a filin wasa na Westbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare zai iya tara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya sami kulawa daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar rahoton West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, wannan ne karo na biyu da Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Republican na Majalisar Dattawa na West Virginia, wanda ba shi da kyau a cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don kokarin inganta martabarsa a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar rahoton Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta nuna gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a wasannin da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman uku na zaman kai, hudu a ranar Asabar da yamma na iya zama abin da ake buƙata a wannan gasar Ryder.
Rashin motsa jiki shine ainihin ra'ayi a wasanni, amma daya daga cikin wadanda 'yan wasan suka gaskanta, musamman a wasanni kamar wannan.
Wane ne suke tsammani yana da ƙarfin hali a yanzu?
"Sun ci gaba da ci shida, yanzu sun ci hudu, don haka za mu iya cewa muna da nasara", in ji Jordan Spieth a kan tashi.
Turai tana da fifiko, maki hudu, da sauran 12.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, duk da haka sun yi imanin cewa suna da iska a cikin fuka-fuki, kuma akwai abubuwa da yawa da ke ba su ƙarfafawa, ciki har da siffofin Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu ya ɗauki maki uku daga cikin yiwuwar hudu.
Spieth ya yi fice daga farko zuwa karshe kuma yana nuna misali.
Muryoyin murna sun kara daɗaɗawa a zagayensa, har ya buga bugun ƙwallo a wasan da aka buga a karo na huɗu lokacin da shi da Thomas suka rage biyu da biyu.
An yi wa wasan kwallo 15 da ya ci kwallo 15 da shi, wanda ya nuna cewa akwai fatan samun nasara a gasar.
"Kawai ka ba da iyakar ƙoƙarinka kuma ka kula da gwagwarmayarka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya rage ga 'yan wasan.
Akwai ramuka 18 da za su iya kawo ɗaukaka.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, babu shakka babban labarin Ryder Cup.
Wasu 'yan Turai da ba a saba gani ba sun ci wasanni hudu kuma ba su yi kuskure ba.
'Yan wasan 'Mollywood' ne kadai suka yi wasan babu buga kwallo a ranar Asabar da yamma, kuma sun guje musu a safiyar Asabar, da yammacin Juma'a da kuma ragowar ramukan tara na ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wasan da suka nuna a yanzu da kuma yadda suke musayar makamashi da masu sauraro masu saurin sauti sun tabbatar da cewa sun kasance manyan masu son wasannin ranar Lahadi kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari farin ciki da zai iya daukar nasarar Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a filin wasan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau idan duka biyun suna cikin ramuka daban-daban a lokaci guda.
Amma, ba a san lokacin da za a yi bikin Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi gaggawar doke Sergio Garcia, gwarzon dan wasan kwallon kafa hudu da suka buga a safiyar yau, a wasa daya da Alex Noren.
Wani bugun daga cikin kwallo da biyu a ramuka tara na farko sun binne dan kasar Spain da kuma dan kasar Sweden a cikin ramin da ba su iya fita daga ciki ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka ka fita daga raminka.
Wasan kwallon kafa hudu da hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallon su a kusa saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a wani lokaci.
Turai ta yi fice a matsayin kungiya kuma tana da babban ci gaba a ranar karshe, amma wannan zaman na hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da sha'awar yin gwagwarmaya da wasu suka yi shakkarsa, musamman a nahiyar Amurka.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta shiga gasar Ryder ta karshe da gagarumin ci gaba, bayan da ta ci gaba da cin nasara a kan Amurka da ci 10 da 6 a wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, sun fara jagorantar da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods, wanda ya kara da maki hudu a filin wasan Le Golf National.
A gasar da suka yi a gidan wasan golf na Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, 'yan Turai Thomas Bjorn sun doke 'yan Amurkawa da suka yi wasa a wasan da safe da kwallon hudu, kuma sun ci wasan da ci uku da daya.
Amurka ta yi nasara a gasar zakarun Turai, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage ragin ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk tana bukatar ta samu maki takwas a wasanni 12 da za ta buga a ranar Lahadi domin ta ci gaba da rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine dan wasa na farko a Turai da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda ake kira Molliwood bayan wata kyakkyawar karshen mako, sune kawai ma'aurata biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka ci kwallaye hudu a farkon wasanninsu hudu.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan da aka yi da hudu, sun yi wasa sosai, sun shawo kan Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka, Bryson Dechambeau, da ci 5 da 4.
Woods wanda ya shawo kan wasannin biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi ta haskakawa a wasu lokutan, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin 29 da ya buga a wasan da hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a wasan safiya na hudu, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henry Stenson a gasar hudu kuma ya sha kashi 2-1 daga Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepke  na farko da na uku a duniya.
Amma duk da haka, ba abin da ya faru a Turai a wannan rana mai kyau a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa Amurkawa maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sha wahala sosai sun ci nasara da 2-1, a kan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan hudu, don daga baya su dawo su doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4-3 a hudu, bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta dawo bayan ta yi kasa da maki hudu a wasan da ta buga, duk da cewa Fury da ke kare kofin ya ci wasan ne kawai don ya ci gaba da rike kofin.
Amma bayan sun yi kwana biyu a matsayi na biyu, ba za su iya kai farmaki a ranar Lahadi ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce za ta iya yin watsi da makaman ta idan ba ta amince da juna ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa tsawaita takunkumi ya kara tsananta rashin amincewar da take da ita ga Amurka kuma a irin wannan yanayi kasar ba za ta taba yin watsi da makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Hu ya shaida wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na nuna kyakkyawan buri" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman rokoki, rushe tashar nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin cewa ba za ta kara yawan makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, babu wani martani da ya dace daga Amurka", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, babu wata hanyar da za mu fara yin amfani da makamai a cikin gida".
Duk da cewa Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafin Koriya ta Arewa game da juriyar Washington game da "mataki-mataki" na kawar da nukiliya wanda zai ba Koriya ta Arewa lada don matakan da ta ɗauka, mahimmancin bayanin nasa shi ne cewa bai yi watsi da haramtacciyar hanyar nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne kan wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko da shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa suka yi a Singapore ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "yantar da yankin Koriya daga nukiliya", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin ba Koriya ta Arewa tabbacin tsaro.
Koriya ta Arewa na son kawo karshen yakin Koriya (1950-53), amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara mika makamashin nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi watsi da kira da ake yi na sassauta takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ba ta daina 'denuclearisation first' kuma tana kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar karfi, har ma da 'ƙaddamar da ƙarshen yaƙi,' " in ji Ri.
"Tunanin cewa takunkumi zai iya durƙusa mana a ƙasa mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, tsawaita takunkumi yana kara tsananta mana rashin amincewa.
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron karawa juna sani tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya nuna ganawa uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: "Idan da mun tattauna wannan batun batun nukiliya tare da Koriya ta Kudu, ba tare da Amurka ba, to, nukiliya ta yankin Koriya ba za ta zo cikin irin wannan halin da ba ta da mafita".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Rio ya bambanta da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya fadawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da Amurka ta kai kan kasar Koriya ta Arewa da makamai masu linzami ba zai yiwu ba bayan da "Mista Shugaba Trump" ya kira Kim "Mokamin Makami mai linzami" a kan wani aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen kawar da makaman, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta aiwatar da haramtacciyar makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce bai kafa wani lokaci ba, yana cewa: "Idan ya zama dole, bari ya kasance shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar.
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci Pyongyang ta ba da lada kan matakin da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Dole ne a ci gaba da tsaurara takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro kuma ba tare da sassautawa ba har sai an cimma cikakken, karshe, tabbatar da haramtacciyar makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro ya amince da takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 domin hana Pyongyang samun kudaden da za ta kashe a fannin makaman nukiliya da kuma makaman nukiliya.
Pompeo ya gana da Riya a wajen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
A watan Yuli, ya bar Pyongyang yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, kuma Koriya ta Arewa ta yi masa kashedi bayan sa'o'i kadan saboda yin "buƙatun 'yan daba".
A wata ganawar da suka yi da Moon a watan jiya, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta rushe tashar makaman nukiliyarta da kuma tashar makaman nukiliyarta idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da ake bukata sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matakai don daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard suna yin darasi a kan yadda za su samu isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya yi niyyar sa dalibai su kara samun karin bacci a kokarin kawar da al'adun maza masu karantar dare da dare da ake amfani da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya lura cewa ɗaliban manyan jami'o'i a duniya ba su san yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya kirkiro wani tsari da ya yi imanin cewa shi ne kadai a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don fara wannan darasi bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci akan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa za ka gaya mini wannan a wannan shekarar da nake makarantar sakandare?"
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki, in ji shi ga The Telegraph.
A wannan shekarar, an gabatar da darasi na farko ga ɗalibai game da yadda samun isasshen barci zai taimaka musu su sami ci gaba a makaranta da kuma wasanni.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a makarantar likitancin Harvard da kuma shugaban jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan da aka lura cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci sosai a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na sa'a daya ya kunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashi akwai hoton wani ɗaki a ɗakin kwanan dalibai, kuma ɗalibai za su danna kan kofunan kofi, labule, takalma da littattafai don ƙarin koyo game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, da kuma tasirin rashin bacci kan wasan motsa jiki da kuma mahimmancin al'ada kafin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta cewa rashin barci na dogon lokaci na iya kara hadarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, bakin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar makarantar da gumakan da ke cikinta suna ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa hakan ba zai canja halin ɗaliban nan da nan ba.
Amma mun yi imani suna da 'yancin sanin hakan kamar yadda kuke da 'yancin sanin sakamakon shan taba a kan lafiyarku, in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adun alfahari da "barcin dare" na ci gaba, in ji shi, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da matsin lamba ga dalibai ya sa rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Ya ce, samun isashen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na ɗalibai wajen magance damuwa da gajiya da kuma damuwa, har ma da yin nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwarsu ta shiga yanayin yunwa kuma hakan yana sa su ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan shekara 19 da ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilmin kimiyyar halittu a California, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin laccocinsa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard a bara.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya yi kira ga ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin harabar makarantar.
Yana fatan cewa mataki na gaba shi ne a bukaci dukkan daliban da suka kammala karatunsu su bi irin wannan tsarin karatun kafin su shiga wata jami'a mai gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da saita ƙararrawa don lokacin bacci da farkawa da kuma kula da mummunan tasirin "hasken shuɗi" wanda allon lantarki da fitilun LED ke fitarwa kuma zai iya lalata sautin circadian, don haka haifar da matsalar bacci.
Livingston 1  0 Rangers:
Rangers sun sha wani mummunan rauni a gidan bayan da Dolly Meng ta jefa kwallo ta tura Steven Gerrard da aka yi wa kwallo a 1-0 da Livingston.
'Yan wasan Ibrox sun nemi nasarar su ta farko a gida bayan nasarar da suka samu a watan Fabrairu da ci 4-1 a St Johnstone, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta sha kashi na biyu a hannun Gerrard a wasanni 18, inda ta bar tawagarsa ta kai maki takwas a ragar 'yan wasan Ladbrokes, Hearts.
Meng ya zura kwallo da minti bakwai kafin rabi, kuma Rangers ba su taba kusa da daidaitawa ba.
Yayin da Rangers ta fadi zuwa ta shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa ta uku, kuma suna baya da Hibernian ta hanyar raga kawai.
'Yan wasan Rangers na iya fuskantar wasu matsaloli bayan da alkalin wasa Calum Spence ya nemi taimako bayan da aka harbe shi da wani abu daga gefe.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a tawagar da ta wuce Ayr kuma ta kai wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar Betfred.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya yanke shawarar daukar 'yan wasan Livingston 11 da suka ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda tawagarsa ta matsa wa abokan hamayyarta a kowane mataki.
Wataƙila Rangers sun mamaye mallakar ƙwallon ƙafa, amma Livingston ya yi amfani da lokacinsa da ƙwallon ƙafa.
Sun kusa cin kwallo mintuna biyu bayan da Meng ya fara karawa a raga ya tura Scott Pittman a raga na Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya rasa babbar dama kuma ya buga kusa da kwallon.
Keagan Jacobs ya buga kwallo mai zurfi, sai ya samu kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin hamayyarsa Alan Lithgow ya samu damar buga kwallo a raga a gaban raga.
Rangers sun samu nasarar karbe ragamar wasan, amma wasan da suka buga a kashi na uku na karshe ya nuna cewa suna da bege fiye da yadda suke da imani.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi tunanin cewa ya kamata ya samu bugun daga minti 15 lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo, amma alkalin wasa Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da bukatar ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun samu kwallo biyu ne kawai a raga a farkon rabin wasan, amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox, Liam Kelly, ya kare bugun da Lassana Coulibaly ya yi a kai ba tare da wata matsala ba, kuma ya rage bugun da Ovie Ejaria ya yi.
Ko da yake burin farko na Livingston a minti na 34 ba zai iya nuna ainihin ƙarfin ƙarfin wasan ba, babu wanda zai iya jayayya cewa ya cancanci, idan ba wani abu ba, to, saboda ƙoƙarin da aka yi.
Rangers sun sake kasa cin nasarar kwallo mai zurfi da Jacobs ya buga.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai natsuwa kuma ya zaɓi Meng don kammala wasan.
Gerrard ya amsa ga katsewar ta hanyar gabatar da Ryan Kent a madadin Coulibaly kuma wannan maye gurbin ya yi tasiri kusan nan take lokacin da dan wasan ya yi amfani da Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya gudu daga layinsa kuma ya toshe shi.
Duk da haka, Livingston ya ci gaba da sa baƙi su yi wasa daidai yadda suka dace da su, tare da dogon Lithgow da Halkett.
Holt da tawagarsa sun samu damar karawa juna karfi a minti na karshe, amma McGregor ya ci gaba da tsayuwa, ya kare harin da Jacobs ya kai, sannan Lithgow ya jefa kwallo a kusa da kwallo daga kusurwa.
Dan wasan Rangers Glenn Middleton, a karshen wasan ya nemi karin fanareti daya lokacin da ya yi karo da Jacobs, amma Thomson bai sake amsawa ba.
