Johnny English ya sake aiki  mai laushi ɗan leƙen asiri mai ban dariya tare da Rowan Atkinson
An riga an yi al'adar neman rubutun Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim mai taken Burtaniya, wanda za a iya amfani da shi ga wannan ci gaba na kamfen ɗin satirical na Johnny English  wanda ya fara tun 2003 tare da Johnny English  kuma ya dawo kan allon a cikin 2011 tare da Johnny English: sake haihuwa .
Shin, wani irin baƙar magana game da yadda ba mu da amfani zai zama sabon damar fitar da kaya ga al'ummarmu?
Ko ta yaya, mai kallo, mai iya magana Johnny English mai fuskar roba ya sami wata dama ta sake yin wani abu  wanda sunansa ya nuna fiye da komai cewa shi ne zane-zane na zane-zane wanda aka tsara don yankunan da masu sauraron fina-finai ba su da harshen Turanci.
Wannan, ba shakka, wani ɗan leƙen asiri ne wanda duk da cewa yana da kyawawan halayen da ke nuna cewa yana da kyau, yana da ɗan Clouseau, da ɗan Mr. Bean, da ɗan saurayin da ya buga waƙa guda a cikin taken "Chariots of Fire" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Hakanan an fara shi ne bisa matafiyi da kuma wani mutum na duniya wanda ke lullube da asiri wanda Atkinson ya taba yin fim a cikin tallace-tallace na Barclaycard TV da aka manta da su, ya bar rikici a baya.
Wani abu ko biyu daga cikin sabon aikinsa yana da kyau.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa kan jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu sanye da kayan ɗamara na jarumi da kuma yadda wutan rotor ke saurin ratsa kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson's talent for physical comedy is obvious, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana da rauni kuma a cikin wani abu mai ban mamaki wanda ba shi da amfani, musamman ma yanzu da manyan fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna da tabbacin ƙarawa da abubuwan ban dariya.
Na san cewa wannan wasan kwaikwayo ne ga yara, ba ga manya ba, kuma a gare ni, Johnny English ba shi da kwarewa da kuma zane-zane kamar Atkinson ba tare da yin fim ba.
Yanzu magana ce ta yau da kullum cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan leken asiri ya kutsa cikin wata babbar kungiyar leken asiri ta Burtaniya, ya bayyana sunayen dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a fagen, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aiki - rashin alheri, karamin rawa ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shine ruwa na karshe a cikin gilashin ruwa ga firaminista, mai girman kai da kuma halin da ya riga ya kasance a cikin mummunan lalacewa saboda rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thomson ta yi wasa da kyau a cikin wannan halin da aka tsara bisa ga Theresa May, amma rubutun ya kasance mai banƙyama.
Masu ba ta shawara a harkokin sirri sun sanar da ita cewa an lalata dukkan 'yan leken asiri da ke aiki kuma za ta bukaci daukar wani daga cikin wadanda suka yi ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English mai banƙyama, wanda yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata babbar makarantar, amma yana ba da darussan da ba a san shi ba game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa lokacin da Turanci ke gudanar da makarantar leƙen asiri a cikin fim ɗin "School of Rock".
An mayar da Ingilishi zuwa Whitehall don umarnin gaggawa da kuma sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa mai haƙuri Bough, wanda aka sake buga shi da Ben Miller.
Bough yanzu ya zama miji, ya auri kwamandan jirgin ruwa wanda ke da ƙarfin hali da kuma rawar da Vicky Pepperdine ke yi.
Don haka Batman da Robin don yin abubuwa ba daidai ba sun sake yin aiki da sabis na sirrin Sarauniya kuma suna farin cikin kyakkyawar matar mutuwa Ophelia Bullet, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta yi.
A halin yanzu, firaministan kasar ya fada cikin tarkon wani mai karfin kudi mai karfin gaske wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Walt, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara aikin wasan kwaikwayo: suna yin kama da masu ba da abinci, sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa, suna haifar da rikici ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwa na Walton, kuma Turanci ya haifar da rikici ta hanyar ƙoƙarin shiga cikin gidan Walton ta hanyar amfani da belun kunne na gaskiya.
A bayyane yake cewa an yi ƙoƙari sosai a wannan fim ɗin na ƙarshe, amma duk da cewa yana da daɗi da farin ciki, fim ɗin gaba ɗaya kamar an yi shi ne don yara.
Yana da inganci mai kyau.
Kamar yadda yake a sauran fina-finan Johnny English, ba zan iya guje wa tambayar kaina ba: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya za ta iya samar da wani rawar da za ta nuna baiwar Rowan Atkinson?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana da wani shiri ga 'yan Birtaniya da za su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, kuma a biya su albashi na kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour za ta yi nazari kan wani tsari mai tsattsauran ra'ayi wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, amma a biya su albashi na kwana biyar.
A cewar jam'iyyar, shuwagabannin kamfanoni na son ma'aikatan su samu karin lokacin da suka samu daga fasahar kere kere ta hanyar ba su karin rana daya.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikatan su ji daɗin hutu na kwana uku amma su ci gaba da samun albashi ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi zai dace da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin inganta yanayin aiki da kuma kare hakkin ma'aikata.
An amince da sauya zuwa mako hudu na aiki a majalisa ta kungiyar kwadago a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata zasu iya amfani da tattalin arzikin da ke canzawa.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa ana sa ran fitar da sabuwar manufar kafin karshen shekara.
Ba zai faru cikin dare ba, amma aikin kwana hudu a mako babban buri ne wanda ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arzikin da ke amfanar ma'aikata, da kuma dabarun masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba daya.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da za ta amince da wannan ra'ayin ba, saboda Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin yin aiki kwana hudu a mako a lokacin yakin neman zaben shekarar 2017.
Amma wannan burin ba shi da goyon bayan jam'iyyar Labour baki daya.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Ba siyasa ba ce jam'iyyar ta yi amfani da ranar aiki ta kwana hudu a mako kuma jam'iyyar ba ta yin la'akari da hakan".
Shugaban jam'iyyar adawa John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa game da juyin juya halin zamantakewar tattalin arziki.
Mr. McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar kwace iko daga hannun shuwagabannin da ba na mutum ba da kuma masu amfani da ayyukan gwamnati.
