Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na ta'addanci
Mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a jaridar U.S. Daily, tana jinjinawa Amurka da China kan amfanin cinikayya, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi magana game da wani sabon shafi na jaridar China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a yi a ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, wanda China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa wannan sabon mataki ne a wani yunkuri da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Kuma yayin da yake al'ada ne ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su fitar da tallace-tallace don inganta cinikayya, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani inda suke karawa juna haraji kan shigo da kayayyaki.
A matsayin wani mataki na juriya, a baya, harajin da China ta sanya a wannan yakin cinikayya ya shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa wanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, masana kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon magajin garin Iowa, wanda shine babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata sanarwa da aka buga a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, "Yanzu tana ninka wannan tashin hankali ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridunmu".
"A cikin yada farfagandar sa, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da' yancin manema labarai ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace a jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a kan kiosk da ke nan a kan titi a Beijing, za ku sami iyakantaccen adadin ra'ayoyi daban-daban kuma ba za ku iya ganin ainihin ra'ayoyin da mutane a China za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, la'akari da cewa kafofin watsa labarai na kasar Sin suna karkashin karkiyar jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa "wani daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ya ki bayar da shawarar buga" labarinsa, ko da yake bai bayyana jaridar da ya rubuta ba.
'Yan Republican na hana mata kada kuri'a a gaban zaben tsakiyar shekara da aka yi da Kavanaugh, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa
Masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa manyan 'yan Republican da ke karewa da kuma goyon bayan dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar tuhume-tuhume da dama na zargin cin zarafin mata, za su fuskanci mummunan sakamako, musamman mata, a lokacin zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
Motsin zuciyar da ke tattare da wannan batun yana da tsananin gaske kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son yin hakan.
Babu wata hanyar komawa baya a cikin waɗannan abubuwan, "in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a cikin wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) da ya nemi a gudanar da bincike na FBI a karshe zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da gobe ba, ba kuma a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kungiyar MoveOn a Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ihu "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" yayin zanga-zangar da aka yi a cikin zauren majalisar dattijai, yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da Kwamitin Shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Democratic himma da kuma dalili zai zama m", ya ce da labarai Stu Rothenberg, m siyasa Analyst.
Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya tsayi, kuma gaskiya ne.
