Tun kafin shaida ta Ford a gaban jama'a inda ta bayyana dalla-dalla game da zargin cin zarafin wani dan takarar kotun koli, masu bincike sun yi tunanin cewa za a iya samun mummunan sakamako idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da nadin.
"Wannan ya zama babban rikici ga tsohuwar jam'iyyar", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican, a wannan makon.
"Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe, ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai zama alkali, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka magance wannan batun da kuma yadda suka bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan kungiyar da ke goyon bayan zaben 'yan Democrat, Priorities USA.
Duk da haka, jama'ar Amurka sun rabu da juna game da wanda za su yi imani da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, suna karkatar da kai ga Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na mutanen da aka yi wa bincike sun amince da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka amince da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh yana iya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce suna jin haka game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya fara, FBI na ci gaba da binciken zargin da Ford da kuma akalla wani mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, suka yi, in ji jaridar The Guardian.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
