An zargi dan wasan gaba na Portugal da Juventus da yiwa wata Ba'amurkiya mai suna Kathryn Mayorga fyade a dakin otal din Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
An ce ya biya ta dala 375,000 don ta rufe labarin, Der Spiegel ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
Da yake jawabi ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 a wani bidiyo da aka wallafa a shafin Instagram Live, sa'o'i kadan bayan rahoton zargin, Ronaldo, mai shekara 33, ya soki rahoton da ya kira labaran karya.
