Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
A sakamakon katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga lardin Donggale ba, yankin da ke arewacin Palua wanda ya fi kusa da mahaifar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙanƙanin ƙauye a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afkawa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, wacce ke da matsayi na ƙananan yanki, tana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi suna cikin Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Indonesiya.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma addabi Donggala ta yamma a shekarar 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific da ke fama da girgizar ƙasa kuma ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa.
Waɗannan su ne manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata guguwar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi girma a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a gaɓar teku ta kudu kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 30 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haddasa rushewa da firgici domin ta tunatar da mutane da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta auku a shekarar 2004.
Amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a lokacin da gine-ginen suka rushe.
2018. Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na ƙasar Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine, kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun makale a wani lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sara Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin iyalansa
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne bisa zargin hari.
Palin, mai shekaru 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, an kama shi ne bisa zargin aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, hana bayar da rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma tsayayya da kama shi, a cewar rahoton da hukumar 'yan sanda ta Alaska ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran' yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin aikata laifuka, ya kwace wayarta.
An tsare Palin a gidan yari na Mat-Su kuma an ba shi belin dalar Amurka 500.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar inda ya amsa tambayar da aka yi masa game da laifinsa inda ya ce "ba shi da laifi", in ji wannan kafar.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin yana fuskantar hukuncin daurin shekara guda da tara da dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake yankewa hukuncin daurin kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka gabatar da tuhumar aikata laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da laifin kai hari kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton zargin cewa an yi mata fyade.
Yanzu haka dai ana shari'ar ne a kotun sojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar makamai cikin maye da suka shafi lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
An soki Sarah Palin da kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a shekarar 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da PTSD bayan aikinsa a Iraki.
